title: 2BR apt | Spacious living room | LUX vanity + bath | Modern kitchen
posting_body: ['Our spacious studios, one, two and three bedroom apartments are noticeably larger than neighboring apartment communities.', 'With a large air conditioned living room, private deck and ceiling fans, mirrored closet doors and built-in closet organizers in every bedroom, you’ll be living in comfort.', 'This apartment features:', 'Lots of afternoon sunlight!', 'Spacious living and dining room with great room feel', 'Fully-equipped kitchen with stove, refrigerator, dishwasher & disposal', 'Stainless steel appliances', 'Luxurious bath', 'Large balcony', 'Wood-style flooring in kitchen, dining, & bath', 'Plush carpeting in living & bedroom', 'Come Visit us!', 'Park Terrace', '860 Quince Ave', 'Santa Clara, CA 95051', '<URL>', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours', 'Tuesday - Friday 9:00AM to 6:00PM', 'Saturday 9:00AM – 2:00PM', 'Closed Sunday & Monday', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.', 'related search terms ::: santa clara, hwy 280, lawrence expy, san tomas expy, kaiser, pets, santa clara unified school district, pomeroy elementary, cabrillo middle school, santa clara high school']
